{"tid":1840470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］香港人自救方法","createTime":"2020-01-24T23:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T23:52:52.000Z","uid":145863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7825428431cd8fe06ecc8f4a3186efcf112b91","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:41:16.000Z","msg":"事到如今，我地無謂再自己呃自己話岀面既一切係正常。<br />\n香港被打開雙手擁抱支那病人，<br />\n一早已經唔再安全。<br />\n所以香港人自救，<br />\n一定要實行<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全港三罷</span></strong></span>，<br />\n實行<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自我隔離</span></strong></span>(isolation)。<br />\n唔好再FF可以正常反工岀街見朋友娛樂，<br />\n口罩唔係萬能，<br />\n你睇醫護人員包到咁都中招。<br />\n親年放假想去戲院睇戲？支持子華神？<br />\n有無諗過要同一大班人坐咁近成個幾鐘，<br />\n就算大家有口罩都有風險。<br />\n要記住<span style=\"color: red;\">今次病毒極有可能係空氣傳染(airborne)</span>，<br />\n而且<span style=\"color: red;\">一開始病徵極不明顯</span>。<br />\n睇個戲娛樂下，<br />\n分分鐘你就變緊密接觸者。<br />\n除非你包場，咁你stay係屋企睇netflix睇小鴨免費包埸咪仲好。<br />\n同樣道理，接觸身邊既同事朋友家人都唔安全，<br />\n因為你唔會知，甚至佢地都唔會知自己係帶菌者。<br />\n住係同一個屋頂下既就無得好講，<br />\n但唔係必要既呢段危險非常時期就唔好見住了，保留命仔要緊。<br />\n最後，如果大家都做到盡量減少岀門，<br />\n個個stay係屋企，<br />\n香港變成城，經濟生意衰到貼地，<br />\n自然就會比到無能政府壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全港三罷，<br />\n自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n停駛高鐵，<br />\n限制入境。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，<br />\n時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，<br />\n缺一不可。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"26b5eb1b4d8a692313fa4ae5e623f87c5dded1ef","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:43:14.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"7e3ea5381d6a7db08bb759a2634a4a542fc3d98b","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:43:27.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"e64cc17762bb05dedf0e48875b5928be46011335","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:43:50.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"1e97bb5d07d8bfcde04e539dfb005e237262e7b3","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:44:04.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"83029441e81a581f7695a1b89379b0941cc6d2ce","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:44:37.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"cc6b4ce19f05008cb0929f46e943b5cafbb7f978","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:45:55.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"e7e8033509f22a02a42e5ab2e65176a1264dd7e9","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:48:31.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"b044c0c49a594f7efba46accce07b429e0cad4e0","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:50:15.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"d59f4b37776b03e4885785e650348de872c2d1df","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:51:42.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"580609e6a084ec33e20176068478e9977d6e3afe","tid":1840470,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"自推10"}]}